<plot>Winner of the Farewell Routemaster Film Challenge, commemorating the end of the Routemaster bus commuter service, "Bus Kong" is an animation that exploits the iconography of the Routemaster, London and "King Kong", pitching our hero against a bendy-bus with teeth and the sinister Mayor of London.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?087390</url></doc>
